snippet.title: Legends of Ethernal Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Legends of Ethernal is a single-player 2D action/adventure game to be released on August 20th, 2020, on Steam and consoles.

Wishlist our game on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/908480/Legends_of_Ethernal/

Follow us on our social media at
- Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ldstudiomtl/
- Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/ldstudiomtl/
- Twitter: https://twitter.com/ldstudiomtl
